Justice has been done, to a point.  The guild to which he belonged finally disguilded him in Butcherblock yesterday.  However, within hours he was in another, honorable guild.  The moment I knew whom, I immediately took steps to inform the officers and guild leader of the snake in their fold. <br>
<br>
As my story, alone, is so incredible, I felt there should be witnesses from my own guild there and the entire conversation was logged.  This thread is the main body of evidence against him, as it is difficult to repeat my story over and over again to explain what a lying weasel this Srir person really is.  His audacity is so incredible that rational people do not believe it.<br>
<br>
