<br>
&quot;Srir is a scumbag.  But don't take my word for it...&quot;<br>
<br>
So that's it.  From here on in, whoever's guild tag Srir is wearing, if I see it, it gets published here, along with a screenshot so there is NO question as to who he is or to which guild he belongs.  I feel this is more than fair.<br>
<br>
You Have Been Warned.<br>
<br>
